flow-state|deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange_physical_rhythm|strength_2|2|Finding original clarity|Deep Focus helps you hold the problem still, while Creative Movement lets the answer shift. This can produce ideas that are both careful and fresh.|creative_movement|active|flow-state::deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange_physical_rhythm::strength_2
flow-state|deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange_physical_rhythm|strength_3|3|Making the idea easier to use|Social Exchange helps you hear what is clear, confusing, or missing. Physical Rhythm can then give you a practical reset before the next round of thinking.|social_exchange|active|flow-state::deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange_physical_rhythm::strength_3
