flow-state|deep_focus_physical_rhythm_creative_movement_social_exchange|strength_2|2|Using pace to support focus|Physical Rhythm gives your concentration a practical base. A walk, routine, change of setting, or steady work cycle can make careful thinking easier to sustain.|physical_rhythm|active|flow-state::deep_focus_physical_rhythm_creative_movement_social_exchange::strength_2
