flow-state|deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange_creative_movement|strength_1|1|Doing careful work that holds up|You can give important work enough attention to make it reliable. This is a strength when mistakes would be costly or when the answer needs to be well founded.|deep_focus|active|flow-state::deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange_creative_movement::strength_1
flow-state|deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange_creative_movement|strength_2|2|Making concentration workable|Physical Rhythm helps you keep attention available through pace, movement, routine, or environment. This can make deep work feel less forced and more repeatable.|physical_rhythm|active|flow-state::deep_focus_physical_rhythm_social_exchange_creative_movement::strength_2
