flow-state|deep_focus_social_exchange_creative_movement_physical_rhythm|strength_2|2|Sharpening thought through response|Social Exchange helps you turn a private view into something clearer. A good question or live reaction can show what your thinking has actually become.|social_exchange|active|flow-state::deep_focus_social_exchange_creative_movement_physical_rhythm::strength_2
